Stephanie and Stevie agree to end their brief romance as she returns to America, and Louise and Fordy cook each other meals for their date.

Riley demands an apology from Jamie, and Lucy is confused by the whole situation with him.

Spencer tells Alex that maybe it’s best if him and Binky split up causing her to make a public announcement for people to stop talking about them

episodes.name: Some People Are Off Limits
episodes.overview: Jamie wants to take Habbs on a date, but is it all getting too much for her? Maeva turns to James for solace when Miles says he can’t see a future with her.

episodes.name: As Far As The Wrongest Thing You’ve Ever Done, This Ain’t That Bad
episodes.overview:
Habbs agrees to go out with Jamie, but a run-in with Sophie Hermann changes her mind.

Verity discovers that feelings may not be mutual between Amelia and Hugo.

Last in the season.

episodes.name: Victoria, I Will Never Die
episodes.overview: The reality show returns, with Maeva finding herself in a complicated situation after kissing both James and Miles on a night out, while Freddie starts dating French girl Jade and enlists the help of Miles for translation purposes.

episodes.name: Right, I’ve Got A Little Bit Of A Situation
episodes.overview: Verity faces a dilemma after Rosi's revelation to her that she'd recently hooked up with Jamie. Should Verity confront Jamie for answers or go straight to Habbs?

episodes.name: This Is Something That Chelsea Lacks – Common Decency!
episodes.overview: After the revelation that Jamie slept with Rosi, Habbs retreats to Liv's house in Henley, while Jamie seeks solace with best friend Alex

episodes.name: I’m The Opposite Of A Narcissist
episodes.overview: Sam Thompson returns to the Chelsea fold and still has an axe to grind with Jamie over his betrayal with Habbs. Are they able to repair their broken friendship?

episodes.name: Who Brought Maeva?
episodes.overview: Jamie is keen to make amends with Sam, but it's not as easy as he'd hoped. Maeva's plans to make James jealous backfire. And Sophie takes Amelia under her wing.

episodes.name: I Don’t Know How Many More Nails We Can Put In The Coffin
episodes.overview: Rosi challenges Miles about his motives for stringing Maeva along. Sam introduces girlfriend Zara to his Chelsea friends. Liv enlists Sophie's help with a shoot.

episodes.name: He Must Be Great In The Sack
episodes.overview: Rosi arranges a trip to Istanbul for Maeva's birthday, but was it a mistake to invite Verity? Sam's off to Turkey with Harry, to get some distance from Jamie.

episodes.name: He Needs To Go To Better Lad School
episodes.overview: Jamie is feeling down after a serious injury to his foot in a dance rehearsal. He then has a furious row with Harry, who has been stirring things up with Sam.

episodes.name: Let’s Break Some Bread
episodes.overview: Verity's crush on Tristan grows after Miles organises a night out with everyone, while Victoria drops back in from Miami for a glass of champagne with Mark Francis.

episodes.name: If Anyone Could Ride A Lion It’s Tristan
episodes.overview: Things get complicated as Tristan is caught up in Verity and Emily's heated exchange. Sam and Jamie's friendship is back on track. Liv has questions for Digby.

episodes.name: The Dudelsack Is Out!
episodes.overview: Maeva's dad is in town and all set to meet James for the first time. But how will Maeva react when she discovers that Miles has been secretly meeting her father too?

episodes.name: Argentina Baby
episodes.overview: Buenos Aires gets off to a dramatic start for Liv and Habbs. Tristan and Verity's romance is blossoming on their trip, but will Miles lead Tristan astray?

episodes.name: I Wish I Was A Narcissist
episodes.overview: After forgiving Jamie, Habbs finds herself in a confusing situation, especially when her ex implies that she is making a big mistake

episodes.name: I Have A Girlfriend... On Paper
episodes.overview: How will Habbs cope with the news that Liv has got involved with Harvey again? Sam isn't faring well with Zara either. But can they work it out or is Sam about to face another lonely Christmas?

episodes.name: Let's Get Married
episodes.overview: As the SW3 cast look set for 2020, can Tristan and James bury the hatchet? Will Liv decide to focus on Harvey or try to salvage her friendship with Habbs? And can Sam and Zara make it to the new year?

episodes.name: End of Yah Quiz
episodes.overview: Matt Edmondson, Mollie King and the entire cast look back on another spectacular year with our favourite residents of SW3. Plus there's the very latest gossip from Jamie and Habbs, and Sam and Zara.

episodes.name: I Need My Binky Back
episodes.overview: The reality show returns and the gang gets together for a catch-up dinner, while Jamie and Habbs are back on track after their dramatic reconciliation in Buenos Aires.

episodes.name: I Like Playing In The Danger Zone
episodes.overview: Emily can no longer deny her spark with Harvey but how will Habbs react? Ollie and Gareth discuss their future. And are Sam and Zara heading for a new crisis?

episodes.name: I Don't Care If It's My Battle Or Not
episodes.overview: Jamie is furious with Emily for her disloyalty towards Habbs. Sam meets the parents. Verity and Tristan hit their first bump in the road: will it be their last?

episodes.name: If You're Secure In Your Relationship, It Shouldn't Be An Issue
episodes.overview: Sam is shocked when he finds out who Miles's new love interest is. Emily reaches out to Habbs. And can Ollie persuade Sophie to look at Fred in a romantic light?

episodes.name: 99% Of The Population Will Understand What I'm Saying
episodes.overview: Zara comes face to face with Sam's ex. Miles and his new love interest are growing closer - but are they on the same page? Jamie admits he isn't feeling himself.

episodes.name: She Doesn't Trust Him To Be Around Me
episodes.overview: Sam tries to cover his tracks. Harvey wants to cement his relationship with Emily, but is she ready to take the next step? Ollie and Binky don't see eye to eye.

19.name: Season 19
19.overview: Familiar faces from the original cast return for a new season that follows the gang reaching a crossroads in their friendships, love lives and more.

episodes.name: 3AM is Prime Time Booty Call
episodes.overview: The gang reunite in the country for a summer of love and luxury. Back in Chelsea, a new revelation rocks Sam and Zara's relationship. And Ollie and Gareth's wedding plans are up in the air.

episodes.name: You're Leaving A Couple Of Vipers For Another Couple Of Vipers
episodes.overview: Zara confronts Melissa. Sam's suspicious when Liv and Tiff invite Zara to their party. New boy Charlie causes a stir. Can Gareth rein in Ollie's wedding plans?

episodes.name: With Great Rig Comes Great Responsibility
episodes.overview: As Verity and Charlie get closer, Maeva returns with a scandalous secret. Zara and Melissa's friendship is on the rocks. Can Ollie find a man for Sophie Hermann?

episodes.name: I Did Something Really Bad
episodes.overview: Tristan struggles as Verity and Charlie continue to grow closer, but is the perfect person to help him move on right in front of him? Zara reveals a secret that shatters Sam's world.

episodes.name: You're My Friend, But I Also Quite Wanna Kiss You
episodes.overview: Tristan's feelings have grown stronger, but does his love interest feel the same? An old rumour risks Tiff and Zara's friendship. Jamie gets Habbs a special gift.

episodes.name: Once The Sex Is Gone, The Relationship Is Gone
episodes.overview: Liv faces up to Verity. Sam returns to Chelsea, but can he forgive Zara and move on with their relationship? Maeva is furious to have her trust broken by Emily.

episodes.name: I Can Get Hard If You Need Me To, Clive
episodes.overview: After their summer of fun in the country, Liv and Tristan hit a stumbling block back in London. Verity and Charlie take a big step. Can Sam and Tiff make amends?

episodes.name: You Get Angry At Your Own Voice
episodes.overview: Liv's torn between Tristan and her new romance. Maeva wants to know how James really feels. Verity confronts Charlie. Sam and Tiff enjoy becoming closer friends.

episodes.name: Crumbs
episodes.overview: The gang head to Cornwall, where Will and Tristan fight for Liv's attention. It's move-in week for Harvey and Emily. Mark-Francis gives Freddie some love advice.

episodes.name: She Just Got A Bit Over Familiar
episodes.overview: An emotional Zara and Sam meet up for the first time since their break-up. Meanwhile, with tensions running high in Cornwall, Tristan makes a dramatic decision.

episodes.name: Ctrl + Alt + Delete Habbs
episodes.overview: Emily's torn between Harvey and Habbs. Can Tiff's advice help Sam and Zara? Things come to a head between Liv and Verity. Ollie and Gareth's wedding takes another hit.

episodes.name: The Wedding
episodes.overview: After months of delays and worry, Ollie and Gareth's big day has arrived. Elsewhere, Tristan makes Liv a tempting offer, and Sam and Zara have a heart-to-heart.

20.name: Season 20
20.overview: The gang takes a long holiday in the country. Sam and Zara's relationship hits a stumbling block. Ollie and Gareth try to plan their dream wedding.

episodes.name: It's Just...Lighting The Match
episodes.overview: Our favourite Chelsea socialites bubble up in a Cotswolds mansion. Ollie and Gareth make an announcement, and the return of Miles and Julius causes a stir.

episodes.name: Stop Spitting On My Mink!
episodes.overview: Tristan questions Julius's motives. Maeva pursues a friendship with her ex, Miles. And are the cracks beginning to show in Reza and Ruby's relationship?

episodes.name: Julius Is Nursing A Semi
episodes.overview: James sees red with Miles. Habbs joins the gang in the Cotswolds. And the surprise arrival of Sophie's love interest, Tom Zanetti, steals Julius's thunder.

episodes.name: I Don't Play Hard To Get
episodes.overview: Miles and Julius are smitten with new girl Inga. Tom gets a grilling about Sophie. And Emily joins the gang, but will things be awkward between her and Habbs?

episodes.name: I've Had More Comfortable Gynaecological Appointments
episodes.overview: Alex and Verity join the group at a country retreat in Suffolk. Emily plans a surprise for Harvey. Miles is caught in the crossfire between Julius and Inga.

episodes.name: The Thing With You Maeva Is You're Just Slightly Misunderstood
episodes.overview: Liv and Maeva take issue with Emily, and sparks fly when Harvey steps in to defend his girlfriend. Miles is confused when Inga seems to be flirting with Alex.

episodes.name: I'm Coming From A Good Place...For Once
episodes.overview: Brand new series: Reza and Ruby are reunited. Tiff tries to convince Liv to make amends with Emily before it's too late. Has Maeva gone too far by warning Inga about Miles?

episodes.name: We've Just Had A Nice Friendly Jacuzzi... What's Up With That?
episodes.overview: Sparks fly after Ruby spends the night in the hot tub with Miles and Julius, and Verity makes a revelation about Reza. Ollie and Gareth have a heart-to-heart.

episodes.name: I'm Moody, If You're Broody
episodes.overview: Ruby plays Cupid for Julius and newcomer Eloise, while Inga is unnerved at the idea of a single girl around Miles. Harvey learns that Emily is feeling broody.

episodes.name: Hurry Up And Break Up With Your Boyfriend
episodes.overview: The gang celebrate Ollie's birthday with a dinner party, but Liv and Tristan are notably absent. Ruby makes a confession to Miles. Emily faces a dilemma.

episodes.name: I Will Skateboard On Your Head
episodes.overview: With their relationship in trouble, will Ruby and Reza go their separate ways? James risks Maeva's wrath. Tom Zanetti treats Sophie to a romantic date.

episodes.name: Prince Charmings Will Come And Go...But I'll Always Be Here
episodes.overview: The gang are back on home turf in Chelsea. Ruby prepares to start a new chapter, while reality sets in for Reza, and Sophie shares some news with Fred.

21.name: Season 21
21.overview: Expect fun, flirting and fireworks as our favourite SW3 socialites escape Chelsea and bubble up in the countryside

episodes.name: Did You Miss Me a Little Bit?
episodes.overview: Did You Miss Me A Little Bit? - A glamorous party brings the whole gang back together in Chelsea, but it is not long before there is a dramatic showdown between Miles and Reza and sparks fly. Maeva takes drastic action. Ollie and Gareth nervously await important news. Tristan starts to move on: how will Liv react?

episodes.name: You're Literally Pouring Gasoline on the Fire
episodes.overview: Liv and Tristan come face to face following their break-up, James takes drastic measures to make Maeva see sense, and Julius expresses an interest in Verity.

episodes.name: I Think You're Dismissed Now
episodes.overview: A heartbroken James tries desperately to fight for his relationship with Maeva, while Tristan's new love interest Nicole attends a girls' night away with Liv.

episodes.name: Trust is Built in Droplets and Lost in Buckets
episodes.overview: Maeva makes an indecent proposal. Angus tries to explain his actions to Paris. And with Tristan's new love interest in attendance, will the fur fly at Liv's birthday party?

episodes.name: I Want a Man Who Buys Me Diamonds, Not Silver
episodes.overview: Nicole and Liv join forces to confront Tristan. Emily and Harvey hit another rough patch. Ruby is unsettled by the idea of Reza hanging out with the new girl Sarrah.

episodes.name: My Heart Was Made Into Beef Carpaccio
episodes.overview: Emotions run high following Emily and Harvey's shock split. Liv wonders whether she and Tristan can give things one last shot. And can Reza keep Sarrah on side?

episodes.name: If They Get Married I Will Eat My Own Scrotum
episodes.overview: Liv and Tristan reveal they are trying to give things another go, Miles finally asks Ruby on a date, while Ruby comes face to face with Reza's potential new love interest Sarrah.

episodes.name: This is a Very Big Red Flag in Front of a Very Scary Bull
episodes.overview: Liv urges Reza to fight for Ruby as Miles and Ruby's romance blossoms. Julius takes Nicole on a date. Ollie and Gareth meet Inga's potential love interest, Ella.

episodes.name: I’m Sorry for Having a Moment of Weakness
episodes.overview: Liv and Tristan take drastic action to reunite Reza and Ruby. Maeva sets Digby up on a date, and Julius is shocked to learn that Nicole is seeing other people.

episodes.name: Big Dig Energy
episodes.overview: Will Ruby be honest with Miles about her feelings for Reza? Inga faces a dilemma. Digby finds himself in the tricky position of liking both Verity and Nicole.

episodes.name: Christmas: I Didn’t Realise How Well Endowed You Were
episodes.overview: The gang swaps Chelsea for a retreat in the Lake District, where Reza and Ruby begin to grow closer again and Verity finds that she and Digby lack chemistry.

episodes.name: Christmas (2)
episodes.overview: As Inga reels from Sam Prince's betrayal, Liv makes a shock discovery about a secret date. Paris takes a big step. Are Reza and Ruby finally on the same page?

22.name: Season 22
22.overview: The Chelsea set are back on home turf for the 22nd series as we follow their lives and loves, from old flames to new flirtations and break-ups to make-ups

episodes.name: She's Like a Snake in Sheep's Clothing
episodes.overview: The gang are back for more drama! Maeva puts the pressure on James after Habbs tells all about her engagement to Jamie. Ruby and Reza are reunited, but Julius isn't happy...

episodes.name: I'm Back
